</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l1">Jch Eberhart vnd ıch <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ker <expan>gebrüde<ex>r</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l2">ıch Mertein <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ker / Tün kunt
                            <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l3">briefe / Als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdig
                        fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l4">Johans Byſchof cʒu <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        vnſer <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l5">cʒwiſchen den
                            <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd
                                <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des Rats </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l6">vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒü
                                <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> allen Jren
                            <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l7">vnd den Jren / vnd vns allen
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / dıenern vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l8">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / ein gütlıch ſteen
                        beredt vnd gemachet hat / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l10">das <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns vnd allen
                        den die auf bede ſeiten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l11"><expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> begriffen
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> verdacht ſein angeen ſol ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l13"> auf <add><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l1">
<del rend="strikethrough">den Criſtabend </del></ab>
<del rend="strikethrough"><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l2">ſchirſt / .
                                </ab></del></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_r2l12">den heılıgen Criſttag ſchierſt </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> der heiligen <expan>cʒwelfbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                            tag Symonis vnd Jude </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l15">ſo der tag an dem himel ıſt / vnd weren ſteen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l16"><expan>beleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſol / bis auf den
                                <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_r2l14">ſant Peters tag
                                    <expan>kathedr<ex>am</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Suntag nach
                        <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l17">
<del rend="strikethrough">Jartag ſchierſt kumend </del> vnd den tag allen /
                        Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l18"><expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir für vns vnd alle
                        die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l19">das gütlıch ſteen alſo aufgenomen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd die
                            <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l20">cʒeite <expan>getrewlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd
                                <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l21">ſüllen / . Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ
                                <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıg<ex>elt</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>aufgedrukt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l25">Jnſıgeln / . <expan>Geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> am <del rend="strikethrough">Montag </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_r2l24"><expan>Mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab></add> nach ſant <del rend="strikethrough"> Gallen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_line_1576486060009_4030">Lucien </ab></add> tag /
                            <del rend="strikethrough">Anno xȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l26">nach Crıſts etc xȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ich, Eberhart, und ich, <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker, <expan>gebrüde<ex>r</ex></expan>,
                        und ich, Mertein <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker, tün kunt
                            <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        briefe, als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdig fürst und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> her Johans, byschof czu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, unser
                            <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, czwischen den
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des rats und
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                        allen iren <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, dienern und den iren und uns
                        allen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, dienern und den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein gütlich steen beredt und gemachet
                        hat, das <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und allen den, die auf bede
                        seiten <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> begriffen
                        <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> verdacht sein, angeen sol <app><note><q type="date">auf <add>den
                            heiligen cristtag schierst</add></q>25.12.1411</note></app>, so der tag an dem himel ist, und
                        weren, steen und <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sol bis <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                                <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>sant Peters tag <expan>kathedr<ex>am</ex></expan>
</add></q>22.02.1412</note></app> und den tag allen. Also <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir für uns
                        und alle die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz wir das gütlich steen also
                        aufgenomen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und die
                            <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> czeite
                            <expan>getrewlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> und süllen. Mit
                            <expan>Urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sig<ex>elt</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>aufgedrukt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> insigeln. <expan>Geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        am <add><expan>mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> nach sant <add>Lucien</add>
                        tag nach Crists etc. xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
